cb.petaltools

Class PetalTool

  • java.lang.Object
    • cb.petaltools.PetalTool

  • public class PetalTool
extends Object
    Convert Rose file into different formats. You'll need to install NSUML to run format=xmi. This code is derived from Test4. This test also shows how to reduce memory consumption by omitting certain nodes when parsing the petal file.
    Version:
    $Id: Test4.java,v 1.5 2001/11/01 15:56:49 dahm Exp $
    Author:
    M. Dahm
